## 🏗️ System Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    classDef user fill:#6366f1,stroke:#4f46e5,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:8px,ry:8px;
    classDef ui fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:8px,ry:8px;
    classDef router fill:#ec4899,stroke:#db2777,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:8px,ry:8px;
    classDef llm fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,rx:8px,ry:8px;

    U(("👤 User")):::user -->|"Uploads & Queries"| UI["🖥️ NeuraFlow UI"]:::ui
    UI -->|"Routes Request"| R["🧠 AI Router"]:::router
    R -.->|"Selects"| G["⚡ Groq"]:::llm
    R -.->|"Selects"| GEM["🔵 Gemini"]:::llm
    R -.->|"Selects"| OR["🌐 OpenRouter"]:::llm
    R -.->|"Selects"| HF["🤗 Hugging Face"]:::llm
```

---

## ✨ Key Features

| Feature | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Multi-LLM Routing** | Intelligent model selection based on task classification. |
| **Fallback Engine** | Automatic failover to secondary models preventing downtime. |
| **PDF Analysis** | Extract, chunk, and analyze large documents seamlessly. |
| **Kubernetes Ready** | Production deployment with auto-scaling and load balancing. |
| **CI/CD** | Automated workflows for testing, building, and validation. |
| **Monitoring** | Live health checks and Prometheus metrics integration. |

---

## 🏛️ Architecture & Tech Stack

### 🧠 AI & LLM
- **Gemini**: Advanced reasoning and context retention.
- **Groq**: Ultra-fast inference and execution.
- **OpenRouter**: Access to top-tier reasoning models.
- **Hugging Face**: Specialized research and experimentation workflows.

### 💻 Backend
- **Python**: Core logic and system orchestration.
- **Streamlit**: High-performance, interactive data application framework.

### ⚙️ DevOps
- **Docker**: Multi-stage, security-hardened containerization.
- **Kubernetes**: Enterprise orchestration and container management.
- **GitHub Actions**: Fully automated CI/CD pipelines.

### 📊 Monitoring
- **Prometheus**: Real-time pod and node telemetry scraping.
- **Health Checks**: Integrated liveness and readiness HTTP probes.

---

## ☸️ Kubernetes & DevOps Excellence

Built for enterprise reliability, NeuraFlow AI features a cloud-native infrastructure:

- **3 Replica Deployment**: Ensures high availability across nodes.
- **Horizontal Pod Autoscaling**: Dynamically scales (2 to 10 pods) based on 70% CPU utilization.
- **Health Monitoring**: Constant liveness validation resolving application stalls.
- **Secrets Management**: Secure API key injection via Kubernetes Secrets.
- **Rolling Updates**: Zero-downtime application upgrades.
- **Load Balancing**: ClusterIP services distributed via Nginx Ingress.

---

## 📈 Performance Metrics

* **99.9% Availability** achieved via intelligent AI failover.
* **2–10 Auto Scaling Pods** responding to traffic surges.
* **Multi-LLM Failover** ensuring zero single points of failure.
* **Health Monitoring** actively tracking cluster stability.
* **Enterprise Infrastructure** ready for cloud-scale deployment.

