## 📂 Project Structure

```text
NeuraFlow-AI/
├── .github/workflows/   # CI/CD (Testing, Docker Build, K8s Validation)
├── app.py               # Streamlit Application Core
├── Dockerfile           # Multi-stage Container Definition
├── k8s/                 # Kubernetes Manifests (Deploy, Service, HPA, Ingress)
├── monitoring/          # Prometheus Configuration
├── requirements.txt     # Python Dependencies
└── README.md            # Project Documentation
```

---

## 🚀 Installation & Deployment

### 💻 Local Setup
```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start application
streamlit run app.py
```

### 🐳 Docker
```bash
# Build the production image
docker build -t neuraflow-ai .

# Run containerized application
docker run -p 8501:8501 neuraflow-ai
```

### ☸️ Kubernetes
```bash
# Deploy all infrastructure manifests
kubectl apply -f k8s/
```

