The repository utilizes rigorous continuous integration and deployment logic:

```text
Push Code
   ↓
GitHub Actions
   ↓
Code Validation & Linting
   ↓
PyTest Unit Testing
   ↓
Docker Image Build
   ↓
Kubernetes Manifest Validation
```

